data.description: Welcome to your next haven at 317 Franchi Way-a blend of modern comfort and upscale features, ideally positioned in the vibrant New Braunfels community.  Distinct Home Highlights:  Corner Lot Splendor: Embrace the added privacy and ample space of this unique corner lot.  Inviting Open Layout: Revel in airy spaces marked by high ceilings, new first floor carpet and paint, creating the perfect ambiance for entertainment and special moments.  State-of-the-Art Kitchen: Delight in culinary adventures with granite countertops, 42" cabinets, a tumbled stone backsplash, and premium stainless steel appliances. Main Floor Primary Retreat: A spacious primary suite with a spa-like en-suite bathroom showcasing a separate tub and shower, topped with a double vanity. Diverse Living Areas: Adapt the additional flex space and game room to fit your lifestyle needs, from a cozy reading nook to a bustling entertainment center. Neighborhood Perks:  New Braunfels is not just a place-it's a lifestyle.  Historic Charm & Modern Amenities: A short drive away from the historic Gruene Hall, shopping districts, and gourmet dining options.  Natural Beauty: Revel in the natural splendors of the Comal and Guadalupe rivers, perfect for a day of tubing, swimming, or fishing. Short drive to Schlitterbahn Waterpark.
